{"root":{"data":{"id":"dgkc0q93jsw0","created":1771645794589,"text":"高中地理必修二"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgkc2j47d1c0","created":1771645935784,"text":"第一章 人口"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgkc8rnsc140","created":1771646424567,"text":"人口的变化，既受自然条件和社会经济条件的影响，\n又对自然环境和社会经济有着重大作用。当今世界存在的\n资源、环境、发展等问题，往往都与人口问题直接关联。\n历史和现实都表明，人口的变化一定要与区域资源环境承\n载力相适应，与社会经济发展相协调。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkc45ysor40","created":1771646063887,"text":"第一节 人口分布"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgkc952007c0","created":1771646453725,"text":"世界人口的分布"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkc9msir3k0","created":1771646492333,"text":"影响人口分布的因素"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgkc9tmlbr40","created":1771646507212,"text":"自然因素"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkc9vbzcrk0","created":1771646510924,"text":"人文因素"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgkc49izh3s0","created":1771646071638,"text":"第二节 人口迁移"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkc4c8nisw0","created":1771646077544,"text":"第三节 人口容量"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkc4jed5i80","created":1771646093126,"text":"问题研究 如何看待农民工现象"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgkc38i28qg0","created":1771645991041,"text":"第二章 乡村和城镇"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgkc4si2fj40","created":1771646112941,"text":"第一节 乡村和城镇空间结构"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkc50vmucw0","created":1771646131176,"text":"第二节 城镇化"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkc542n8uw0","created":1771646138130,"text":"第三节 地域文化与城乡景观"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkc5c30a1s0","created":1771646155566,"text":"问题研究 从市中心到郊区，你选择住哪里"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgkc3e3eggo0","created":1771646003215,"text":"第三章 产业区位因素"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgkc5sqq5u00","created":1771646191829,"text":"第一节 农业区位因素及其变化"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkc5yp9wg00","created":1771646204802,"text":"第二节 工业区位因素及其变化"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkc65vq2i00","created":1771646220429,"text":"第三节 服务业区位因素及其变化"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkc6e4gpnc0","created":1771646238373,"text":"问题研究 实体商店何去何从"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgkc3lrugag0","created":1771646019931,"text":"第四章 交通运输布局与区域发展"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgkc6mmcu600","created":1771646256868,"text":"第一节 区域发展对交通运输布局的影响"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkc6v8hnns0","created":1771646275621,"text":"第二节 交通运输布局对区域发展的影响"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkc73atl940","created":1771646293176,"text":"问题研究 城市交通如何疏堵"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgkc3ueqtpk0","created":1771646038730,"text":"第五章 环境与发展"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgkc7hdle5c0","created":1771646323819,"text":"第一节 人类面临的主要环境问题"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkc7rluviw0","created":1771646346086,"text":"第二节 走向人地协调——可持续发展"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkc80tyieo0","created":1771646366167,"text":"第三节 中国国家发展战略举例"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgkc8a441540","created":1771646386372,"text":"问题探究 低碳食品知多少"},"children":[]}]}]},"template":"default","theme":"classic","version":"1.4.43"}